---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="About Carve Model | Precision Architectural, Film & Product Models in Los Angeles"
  description="Carve Model is a Los Angeles model-making studio crafting architectural models, sales-gallery pieces, product prototypes, film miniatures, and art installations. Turnkey from design to fabrication to installation."
  canonicalPath="/about-carve-model"
  ogTitle="About Carve Model | Los Angeles Model-Making Studio"
  ogDescription="We don't just make models — we help clients visualize, refine, and communicate their vision with confidence."
  active="about"
  imageSlot={true}
>
<Fragment slot="head">
<style>
.page-hero{padding-top:clamp(3rem,6vw,5rem);padding-bottom:clamp(2.5rem,4vw,4rem);}
.page-hero h1{margin-top:1.4rem;}.page-hero p{margin-top:1.4rem;}
.about-media image-slot{width:100%;aspect-ratio:16/7;}
.split{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:clamp(2rem,5vw,5rem);align-items:start;}
.split h2{font-size:clamp(1.7rem,2.8vw,2.4rem);letter-spacing:-0.02em;}
.split p{margin-top:1.1rem;color:var(--cm-gray-300);}
.carve-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(5,1fr);gap:1px;background:var(--cm-line-faint);border:1px solid var(--cm-line-faint);margin-top:3rem;}
.carve-letter{background:var(--cm-ink-900);padding:1.8rem 1.3rem;}
.carve-letter .L{font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:var(--w-black);font-size:2.4rem;color:var(--cm-silver);letter-spacing:-0.02em;}
.carve-letter h4{font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:1rem;font-weight:var(--w-semibold);margin-top:0.8rem;color:var(--cm-text-strong);}
.carve-letter p{font-size:0.84rem;color:var(--cm-text-muted);margin-top:0.5rem;}
.who-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:1.5rem;margin-top:2.5rem;}
.who-card{background:var(--cm-ink-900);border:1px solid var(--cm-border);border-radius:var(--r-sm);padding:1.5rem;}
.who-card h4{font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:var(--w-semibold);}
.who-card p{font-size:0.9rem;color:var(--cm-text-muted);margin-top:0.5rem;}
@media(max-width:820px){.split{grid-template-columns:1fr;}.carve-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;}.who-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;}}
</style>
</Fragment>

<main>
<section class="page-hero"><div class="container">
  <span class="eyebrow">About</span>
  <h1 class="display-lg measure">We carve every model with purpose.</h1>
  <p class="lead measure">Carve Model is a Los Angeles-based model-making studio crafting architectural models, sales-gallery pieces, product prototypes, film miniatures, and art installations — built for moments where clarity matters: approvals, presentations, filming, and internal decision-making. We work with architects, developers, general contractors, agencies, production teams, product designers, and artists across the U.S. and Canada.</p>
</div></section>

<div class="container about-media"><image-slot id="about-studio" placeholder="Drop a studio / workshop photo"></image-slot></div>

<section class="section"><div class="container">
  <div class="split">
    <div>
      <span class="eyebrow">Our approach</span>
      <h2 class="mt-3">Built for alignment, not decoration.</h2>
    </div>
    <div>
      <p>Our clients include architects, developers, production designers, agencies, and product teams across the United States and Canada who rely on physical models not as decoration, but as tools for alignment and action.</p>
      <p>Digital tools are powerful — but important decisions are still made around tables, in rooms, and in real space. We focus on what a model needs to clarify, not what it needs to impress. Every model is tailored to its purpose — nothing more, nothing less.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div></section>

<section class="section section--tight"><div class="container">
  <span class="eyebrow">Our name</span>
  <h2 class="display-md mt-3">C·A·R·V·E</h2>
  <p class="muted mt-2 measure">Our name reflects the values that shape every project we deliver. We build with care, accuracy, and pride.</p>
  <div class="carve-grid">
    <div class="carve-letter"><div class="L">C</div><h4>Craft</h4><p>Traditional techniques paired with advanced fabrication.</p></div>
    <div class="carve-letter"><div class="L">A</div><h4>Accuracy</h4><p>Precision at every scale, from massing to detail.</p></div>
    <div class="carve-letter"><div class="L">R</div><h4>Realism</h4><p>Models that read clearly and convince in the room.</p></div>
    <div class="carve-letter"><div class="L">V</div><h4>Vision</h4><p>We help clients communicate intent with confidence.</p></div>
    <div class="carve-letter"><div class="L">E</div><h4>Execution</h4><p>End-to-end delivery, managed entirely in-house.</p></div>
  </div>
</div></section>

<section class="section" style="padding-top:0;"><div class="container">
  <span class="eyebrow">Who we work with</span>
  <div class="who-grid">
    <div class="who-card"><h4>Architecture firms &amp; developers</h4><p>Planning approvals, investor meetings, and sales galleries.</p></div>
    <div class="who-card"><h4>Urban planners &amp; design consultants</h4><p>Masterplans, context massing, and design reviews.</p></div>
    <div class="who-card"><h4>Film production &amp; art departments</h4><p>Previsualization sets and cinematic miniatures.</p></div>
    <div class="who-card"><h4>Product designers &amp; hardware startups</h4><p>Physical mockups from sketches and CAD files.</p></div>
    <div class="who-card"><h4>Artists &amp; cultural institutions</h4><p>Sculptural works and installations, from maquette to final piece.</p></div>
    <div class="who-card"><h4>General contractors</h4><p>Coordination models and presentation pieces for bids and stakeholder buy-in.</p></div>
    <div class="who-card"><h4>Marketing &amp; creative agencies</h4><p>Display models and campaign props for launches, events, and brand activations.</p></div>
  </div>
</div></section>

<section class="section" style="padding-top:0;"><div class="container">
  <div class="cta reveal" style="position:relative;text-align:center;background:var(--cm-black);border:1px solid var(--cm-border);border-radius:var(--r-sm);padding:clamp(3rem,6vw,5rem) var(--gutter);">
    <h2 class="display-md">Let's bring your vision into the room.</h2>
    <p class="muted mt-2" style="max-width:46ch;margin-inline:auto;">Serving clients across the U.S. from our Los Angeles studio. Every project is handled end-to-end.</p>
    <div class="mt-4" style="display:flex;gap:0.9rem;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;"><a class="btn btn--primary btn--lg" href="/contact">Get a Free Quote →</a><a class="btn btn--ghost btn--lg" href="/works">View Our Work</a></div>
  </div>
</div></section>
</main>
</BaseLayout>
